devdoc.details: Controls the creation of child contracts (Building and BuildingData)     Tracks all addresses of the contracts created by this factory contract     Data model is: BuildingDataFactory ---[contains many]---> Building ---[contains many]---> BuildingData

params.uprn: The UPRN to find the corresponding Building contract for

returns._0: The address of the Building contract associated with the given UPRN

params.documentHash: The SHA256 hash of the document to find

returns._0: The address of the BuildingDate contract

params.uprn: The UPRN of the building to find

returns._0: The address of the Building contract associated with the given UPRN

returns._buildingData: All the on chain addresses of the registered building data contracts

returns._buildings: All the on chain addresses of the registered building contracts

returns._0: bool indicating whether the given UPRN is already registered on chain
The address of the BuildingData contract created
